{"tid":2288010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港電台)有機會未能連任的美國總統特朗普據報將於本屆任期最後數周對華再推強硬政策","createTime":"2020-11-16T07:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T09:16:28.000Z","uid":290404,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0329dfb6bef699a0b6742858b2d5a222af5e7d","tid":2288010,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:45:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">有機會未能連任的美國總統特朗普</span></strong>，據報將於本屆政府任期內的最後幾星期，向中國實施多項強硬政策。<br />\n<br />\n美國有政治新聞網站引述消息人士報道，特朗普政府計劃對更多中國企業、中國政府實體與官員，施加制裁或限制，以回應中國涉嫌侵犯新疆和香港人權，或者威脅美國國家安全的行為。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>不過，官員指出，不要期望特朗普政府會在任內最後階段，對台灣有新的重大舉措，或者再關閉中國在美國的領事館。</strong><br />\n<br />\n報道引述美國國家安全委員會發言人說，除非北京改變立場，成為在全球舞台上負責任的一分子，否則未來總統如果改變特朗普的政策，將會是政治自殺。宣稱勝出大選的拜登，過渡小組拒絕評論報道內容。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560248-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560248-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu3psBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=6ac3704d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560248-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5e4c0e21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560248-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"7f25f8e9419d7eea442aa46c55ce06b9c50f587c","tid":2288010,"uid":116960,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得個呢鋪算中立"},{"pid":"d76acc4314a68da4820eecaf879c8e9a7a4658d0","tid":2288010,"uid":33653,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"7f25f8e9419d7eea442aa46c55ce06b9c50f587c","tid":2288010,"uid":116960,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:46:28.000Z","msg":"我覺得個呢鋪算中立"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"字面上佢無錯喎。"},{"pid":"377251cfcebb3e0133ed14e5b4feb9bc645b1da0","tid":2288010,"uid":195164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc